data.description: Nestled in the convenient Deer Valley community, this 2-story home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Upon entrance you will be greeted by the cozy family room and half bath flowing easily through the dining area into the kitchen.  The second floor features a generous master ensuite with a large walk in closet and master bath with a soaking tub. 3 Other spacious bedrooms share a hall bath, making plenty of room for the whole family. Enjoy the quiet cul-de-sac with a private fenced in backyard
